Odůvodnění
The EGCC regulation refers to Member States only, while the partners of cross-border, trans-national and inter-regional cooperation include candidate and third countries, for which the Additional Protocol No.
3 to the European Outline Convention on Transfrontier Cooperation between Territorial Communities or Authorities will be valid, therefore joint EC and Council of Europe efforts are suggested to harmonise the two drafts.
