This amendment is necessary to bring the text into line with the provisions of the new decision on commitology.
Use targets and indicators should be set in addition to risk targets and indicators
It has to be made clear to Member States that the national indicators are in relation to both the health and environmental risks of pesticide use.
It also has to be clear to Member States what the requirements are for public participation in the development, setting, workings and Amendments of national indicators, to be in line with the Spirit of Directive 2003/35/EC providing for public participation.
